                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">自己的书，下个月才会铺货上市。书一出版，总会有遗憾，白纸黑字难收回，错漏之处全赖读者包涵了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1038357572">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1038357572" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1038357572" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1038357572">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Nise/">Nise</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">上穷碧落下黄泉基本就是大众学术。年青人要爱护自己，不要独面大众。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1032071839">
        <div class="comment">
